				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Wgt7w2bSjWJuGnqE1f8Ufw">Hạ nhật ngẫu thành kỳ 1 - 夏日偶成其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Th%E1%BA%A5t-Thuy%E1%BA%BFt/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%C3%ADch-thi/poem-r-MmkBy8mlpLh6OQ2YCLug">Hoạ Nguyễn Quang Bích thi - 和阮光碧詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Th%E1%BA%A5t-Thuy%E1%BA%BFt/author-ZOpZ46P49J3Ico14TJrZJg">Tôn Thất Thuyết</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhan-Nh%C3%A2n-%C3%9Ac/N%C3%B4ng-gia/poem-pLF2a0ExCKd9WVDTT0zuDA">Nông gia - 農家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhan-Nh%C3%A2n-%C3%9Ac/author-R8g8bVr5Z9T3wFADGJsQjw">Nhan Nhân Úc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xung-X%C3%A1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Truy-ho%C3%A0i-Th%C3%A1nh-t%E1%BB%95-hu%C3%A2n-nghi%E1%BB%87p/poem-59ATa6lAhgXOnpjcyqFOYQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Truy hoài Thánh tổ huân nghiệp” - 奉和御製追懷聖祖勳業</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xung-X%C3%A1c/author-apL4dZEfQkzDx1inl6wVQw">Nguyễn Xung Xác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%B1-gia-t%C3%ACnh-giao-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-3pH9RxtWJYj_rfSeNVoIBw">Quốc sự gia tình giao cảm tác - 國事家情交感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-Xuy%C3%AAn-quan-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dYBU0BMWy96tMiL8Yl7EFA">Tam Xuyên quan thuỷ trướng nhị thập vận - 三川觀水漲二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%E1%BA%A7m-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-U69sDiPLqSskahSXkXBJYQ">Tầm Châu - 潯州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-V%C4%83n-Gia/Th%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BA%A1c-Cao-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-DKn_hfzJn-rFUt0QrfcgOA">Thứ Hạc Cao vận - 次鶴皋韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-V%C4%83n-Gia/author-s7lFce4QMpsdltOIzxeCLg">Trần Văn Gia</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-L%C3%A3i/poem-Vc1UVpRNCT1oARnqP0oGrA">Vịnh sử - Phạm Lãi - 詠史－範蠡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/author-U-Qw0U7nLVKqm8kibmDN6g">Hà Ngô Sô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Tr%C6%B0ng/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-quan/poem-l_XCV4jE0JxCSKvcF-D5EQ">Xuất quan - 出關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Tr%C6%B0ng/author-etbB3Ex07HzNoQP-CZPmVA">Nguỵ Trưng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
